snippet.title: Another Princess is in our Castle v0.3.0 - Update Trailer
snippet.description:
It's been a while, but here we are! APiioC v0.3.0 is out on itch.io and Game Jolt!
Now with new mechanics and even a boss fight against the Other Princess!
Hope it's worth the wait, let me know in the comments below.
See you next time! And thanks for your patience and support!
